# swe-swe

## Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `setup` | Configure git, SSH, testing, credentials |
| `debug-preview-page` | Debug web apps using the App Preview debug channel |
| `update-swe-swe` | Update workspace swe-swe files after a version upgrade |
